     C           *DAY      IFLT 20
     C                     Z-ADD@MM       M       30
     C                     ELSE
     C           @MM       ADD  1         M
     C           M         IFGT 12
     C                     SUB  12        M
     C                     ADD  1         @YY
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    D@M
